Below is a **single, clean Markdown documentation** for all your LibreChat ↔ n8n APIs, generated directly from the workflows you uploaded.

Everything is grounded in your actual n8n logic
(company metrics, financial analytics, projects, tasks, and support)

---

# 🧠 LibreChat Enterprise API (n8n Backend)

These webhooks turn LibreChat into a **real company operating system**:

* CEO dashboards
* Financial analytics
* Project management
* Task assignment
* Support desk

All endpoints are **POST** and accept **JSON**.

Base URL:

```
https://YOUR-N8N-DOMAIN/webhook/librechat
```

---

# 1️⃣ CEO Company Metrics

`POST /company-metrics`

Returns the **latest company performance snapshot**.

## Request Body

```json
{
  "profileType": "ceo"
}
```

If `profileType` is not `ceo`, access is denied.

## Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "overall": {
      "employeeCount": 150,
      "activeProjects": 45,
      "customerSatisfaction": 4.6
    },
    "departments": [
      { "name": "Sales", "revenue": 2100000, "target": 2000000 },
      { "name": "Customer Support", "satisfaction": 4.7 }
    ],
    "quarterlyGoals": [{ "status": "achieved" }]
  },
  "summary": "150 employees | 45 active projects | 4.6/5.0 satisfaction",
  "highlights": [
    "Sales exceeded target by 5.0%",
    "1 quarterly goals achieved",
    "Customer Support maintains 4.7/5.0 rating"
  ],
  "dataSource": "mongodb",
  "generatedAt": "2026-01-15T12:11:23.111Z"
}
```

---

# 2️⃣ CEO Financial Analytics

`POST /financial-analytics`

Live finance engine from MongoDB.

## Request Body (LibreChat style)

```json
{
  "period": "last_30_days",
  "_context": {
    "profile": {
      "profileType": "ceo"
    }
  }
}
```

## Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "period": "Live Data (Real-time)",
    "revenue": 520000,
    "expenses": 350000,
    "profit": 170000,
    "profitMargin": 32.6,
    "monthlyTrend": [
      { "month": "2026-01-15", "revenue": 18000, "profit": 5500 }
    ]
  },
  "summary": "Revenue: $520K | Profit: $170K | Margin: 32.6%",
  "insights": [
    "Analysis based on 30 live records",
    "Latest data point from 2026-01-15",
    "Current profit margin is 32.6%"
  ]
}
```

---

# 3️⃣ Create Project

`POST /project-create`

Creates a project in MongoDB.

## Request Body

```json
{
  "name": "LibreChat AI Rollout",
  "description": "Deploy AI to handle internal ops",
  "status": "active",
  "progress": 25,
  "budget": 200000,
  "spent": 50000,
  "startDate": "2026-01-10",
  "deadline": "2026-03-01",
  "managerId": "USR-001",
  "profileType": "ceo"
}
```

## Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Project created",
  "projectId": "PRJ-4821"
}
```

---

# 4️⃣ List Projects

`POST /project-status`

Returns all projects sorted by deadline.

## Request

```json
{}
```

## Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "projects": [
      {
        "projectId": "PRJ-4821",
        "name": "LibreChat AI Rollout",
        "status": "active",
        "progress": 25,
        "deadline": "2026-03-01"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

---

# 5️⃣ Create Task

`POST /task-create`

Creates a task and assigns it to a real user.

## Request Body

```json
{
  "title": "Fix PDF Rendering Bug",
  "description": "Header disappears in CEO reports",
  "assignedTo": "65a0d5fbd9e3f8b91a223c11",
  "priority": "high",
  "status": "pending",
  "dueDate": "2026-01-25"
}
```

## Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Task created successfully",
  "taskId": "65a13b41c92fa2a9b231ffac"
}
```

---

# 6️⃣ Create Support Ticket

`POST /support-ticket-create`

## Request Body

```json
{
  "subject": "PDF template broken",
  "description": "Logo missing on generated documents",
  "priority": "high",
  "userId": "USR-8821"
}
```

## Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "ticketId": "TKT-1705314558123",
    "status": "open"
  }
}
```

---

# 7️⃣ List Support Tickets

`POST /support-ticket-list`

## Customer View

```json
{
  "role": "customer",
  "userId": "USR-8821"
}
```

## Admin View

```json
{
  "role": "admin"
}
```

## Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "count": 2,
  "data": [
    {
      "ticketId": "TKT-1705314558123",
      "subject": "PDF template broken",
      "status": "open"
    }
  ]
}
```

