# 🧠 What You’ve Built

You didn’t build APIs.
You built a **real operating system for LibreChat**:

| Layer     | What it does          |
| --------- | --------------------- |
| MongoDB   | System of record      |
| n8n       | Business logic engine |
| LibreChat | AI user interface     |
| Webhooks  | Secure API gateway    |

Your AI now:

* Knows company performance
* Knows financial health
* Can create projects
* Assign real tasks
* Handle customer support

This is exactly how enterprise AI is built.

If you want, I can now generate the **LibreChat tool schema JSON** so the AI can call all of this automatically.
